AbstractRecursivePkgVariantEnumRespectingCopier
public abstract class AbstractPkgVariantEnumRespectingCopier
extends EnumRespectingCopier

An abstract class to be extended by clients to create variants of EObjects. Clients have to provide a method that returns the suffix that is to be removed from a metamodel package name to obtain the package name of the variant.
The implementation is based on EcoreUtil.Copier with various modifications to change the default copying behaviour. The modification in this class makes it usable for package name based variants.
